    p_sound2: "La version portable comprend un petit assistant, <code style=\"background:rgba(0,212,255,0.1);color:var(--cyan);padding:0.12rem 0.4rem;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.9em\">_windows_audio.py</code> :",
    li_so1: "<code style=\"background:rgba(0,212,255,0.1);color:var(--cyan);padding:0.12rem 0.4rem;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.9em\">open_windows_sound_settings()</code> — ouvre la page Son de Windows.",
